data.title: Kusel
meta_keywords: Meyers Gazetteer of the German Empire
data.meta_description: The historical entry for Kusel, Kusel, Pfalz, Bayern, including parish and jurisdiction information, in the Meyers Gazetteer of the German Empire also known as Meyers Orts- und Verkehrs-Lexikon des Deutschen Reichs.
data.text:
Type St. - Kusel is a Stadt (City).

Lvl I Bay. - Level I shows which Kingdom or State the place is located in. Kusel is located in Bayern.

RB Pfalz - The Regierungsbezirk for Kusel is Pfalz. The Regierungsbezirk is a government district that is in hierarchy between the State and Kreis level.

LG Kaiserslautern - The Landgericht for Kusel is in Kaiserslautern. The Landgericht is where the District Court is located.

BKdo Kaiserslautern - The Bezirkskommando for Kusel is in Kaiserslautern. The Bezirkskommando is the District Military Command. You can look in the BKdo to find military records.

BA Kusel [self] - The Bezirksamt for Kusel is itself. The Bezirksamt is the District Office.

AG Kusel [self] - The Amtsgericht for Kusel is in itself. The Amtsgericht is where the Lower District Court is located.

StdA Kusel [self] - The Standesamt for Kusel is in itself. The Standesamt is where the Civil Registration Office is located.

kath. Pfk. 1 - Kusel has 1 katholisch Pfarrkirche (Catholic parish church).

ev. Pfk. 1 - Kusel has 1 evangelisch Pfarrkirche (Protestant parish church).

Other 1 - Kusel has 1 church that is not an evangelical church, Catholic church, or Synagogue.
